      <span>
        Quickly gather a group of fellow movie lovers and share your place to
        enjoy your favorite movies together.
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="card-info">
      <%= image_tag 'movienight.png' %>
      <h4>Join the Movie Night Community</h4>
      <span>
        Build a reputation as cinema addict in your city and make new friends!
        Join us today and start making movie memories that will last a lifetime.
      </span>
    </div>
</div>


